<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Angular Development</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/node.css"> <!-- Link to your Node.js-specific CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="background-video">
            <source src="https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/3130284/3130284-uhd_2560_1440_30fps.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <div class="hero-overlay">
            <h1>Angular JS Development</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Angular Development -->
<section class="about-angular">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Choose Angular for Your Projects?</h2>
        <p>
            Angular is a cutting-edge framework developed by Google, designed to build dynamic, scalable, and high-performance web applications. It empowers developers to create seamless user experiences with its robust tools and features.
        </p>
        <p>
            At YTRONIX, we leverage Angular's capabilities to deliver tailored solutions for businesses of all sizes. Whether it's a single-page application (SPA) or a complex enterprise solution, Angular ensures flexibility, speed, and reliability.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Features of Angular Development -->
<section class="angular-features">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Key Features of Angular Development</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Two-Way Data Binding</h3>
                <p>Synchronize data between the model and the view effortlessly, ensuring real-time updates.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Component-Based Architecture</h3>
                <p>Build reusable and maintainable components for scalable and modular applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Dependency Injection</h3>
                <p>Efficiently manage dependencies for cleaner, modular, and testable code.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>High Performance</h3>
                <p>Angular's optimized rendering ensures fast and responsive applications for users.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Cross-Platform Development</h3>
                <p>Create web, mobile, and desktop applications using a single codebase.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Comprehensive Tooling</h3>
                <p>Leverage Angular CLI for faster development, testing, and deployment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Progressive Web Apps</h3>
                <p>Build modern web applications that deliver native-like performance and offline capabilities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Server-Side Rendering</h3>
                <p>Enhance SEO and improve load times with Angular Universal for server-side rendering.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>RxJS Integration</h3>
                <p>Leverage reactive programming with RxJS for managing asynchronous data streams efficiently.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Custom Directives</h3>
                <p>Create reusable custom directives to extend HTML functionality and simplify your code.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>State Management</h3>
                <p>Implement robust state management using NgRx or other libraries for scalable applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>Internationalization (i18n)</h3>
                <p>Develop multilingual applications with Angular's built-in internationalization support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>